│  │  ├─ repetition 6 of 8 ↷ Failure threshold [2] exceeded
│  │  ├─ repetition 7 of 8 ↷ Failure threshold [2] exceeded
│  │  └─ repetition 8 of 8 ↷ Failure threshold [2] exceeded
│  ├─ Repeat! ✔
│  │  └─ Repeat! 1/1 ✔
│  ├─ Details... ✔
│  │  └─ Details... :: repetition 1 of 1 ✔
